developer_understanding_on_working: The configuration code retrieves the user stylesheet URI specified in the TranscodingHints. If the URI is not found, it falls back to the superclass method to get the user stylesheet URI.
developer_understanding_on_triggering_fr: The configuration is triggered whenever the getUserStyleSheetURI method is called in the code.
developer_understanding_on_size_impact: The impact of the USER_STYLESHEET_URI configuration option is limited to the specific functionality related to retrieving the user stylesheet URI. It does not have a significant impact on the overall system.
